I think you are reading too much into my post.  I didn&#039;t claim that all federal debt should be eliminated.  My only statement beyond the facts was to wonder if the trend of only increasing and never decreasing (over the last 50 plus years) will ever change.  Safe to read into that that I tend to think it wouldn&#039;t be a completely bad thing for that trend to change, at least just a little bit :-)
